  "concepts": [
    "Tener que + infinitive = to have to do something",
    "Works like 'have to' in English — conjugate tener, then add que + infinitive",
    "Many common verbs are regular -ar, -er, -ir infinitives",
    "Smart strategy: learn tener que first, then add verbs as you go"
  ],
